ColumnTransformation.ColumnTransformation.Expression: CASE WHEN isnull([TABLE_ref]) OR TABLE_ref = '' THEN StrBetween([DIM] ,'[', '.') ELSE TABLE_ref END
CASE WHEN isnull([Column_ref]) OR [Column_ref] = '' THEN StrBetween([DIM] ,'.', ']') ELSE Column_ref END
CASE WHEN ad = 'False' THEN [_id] ELSE [objectSid] end
CASE WHEN [name_old] = 'super' THEN 'admin' WHEN [name_old] = 'contributor' THEN 'designer' WHEN [name_old] = 'consumer' THEN 'viewer' ELSE [name_old] END
upper(CASE WHEN [METHOD] IN ('GET','PUT') THEN (CASE WHEN url LIKE '/dashboards/%' THEN SubString(url,indexof(URL,'/dashboards/', 1)+13,24) ELSE '' END ) ELSE '' END )

Upper(CASE WHEN [METHOD] IN ('GET','PUT') THEN (CASE When url LIKE '/dashboards/%' AND url LIKE '%/widgets/%' THEN ifstring(indexof(URL,'/widgets/', 1) > -1, RIGHT(URL, 24), '') ELSE '' END ) ELSE '' END )

CASE WHEN [METHOD] = 'GET' THEN 'View' WHEN [METHOD] = 'POST' THEN 'Create' WHEN [METHOD] = 'PUT' THEN 'Edit' WHEN [METHOD] = 'DELETE' THEN 'Delete' WHEN [METHOD] = 'PATCH' THEN 'Patch' ELSE 'Other' END
CASE WHEN METHOD = 'GET' THEN '' WHEN METHOD = 'POST' THEN '' WHEN METHOD = 'PUT' THEN '' WHEN METHOD = 'DELETE' THEN '' WHEN METHOD = 'PATCH' THEN '' ELSE '' END
CASE WHEN isnull(lookup([LastUserAction],LastActionDate,_ID, DashUser)) THEN [LASTLOGIN] ELSE lookup([LastUserAction],LastActionDate,_ID, DashUser) END
CASE WHEN isnull([LastActionDate]) THEN daydiff(now(),[LASTLOGIN]) ELSE daydiff(now(),[LastActionDate]) END

TableSqlTransformation.SqlQuery: SELECT DashboardId, max(TRACE.TIMESTAMP) LastActionDate FROM [TRACE] GROUP BY DashboardId
SELECT DashUser, max(TRACE.[TIMESTAMP]) LastActionDate FROM [TRACE] GROUP BY DashUser

SELECT ad._id, ad.Users_adgroups_dim1_idx AS Users_groups_dim1_idx, ad.Users_adgroups AS Users_groups, 'ActiveDirectory' AS Source FROM [Users.Users_adgroups] ad union SELECT ug._id, ug.Users_groups_dim1_idx, ug.Users_groups, 'SisenseUsers' AS Source FROM [Users.Users_groups] ug

SELECT lower(d.Datasource_Address) AS address,d.Datasource_Title AS title , d.ECkey , lower(d.Datasource_Address) + '|' + d.Datasource_Title AS Server_Datasource FROM [DASHBOARDS] d WHERE IsNullOrEmpty(d.Datasource_Address) = false union SELECT lower(e.server) , e.title, Upper(e.ECkey) , e.Server_Datasource FROM [ELASTICUBE] e WHERE IsNullOrEmpty(e.server) = false

Select [_id] [_ID], field_index [ITEM INDEX], jaql_dim DIM, jaql_column [Column_ref], jaql_agg AGGREGATION,jaql_table [TABLE_ref], rankdesc([_ID], jaql_dim) AS DimRank,CASE WHEN isnull([jaql_table]) OR jaql_table = '' THEN StrBetween([jaql_dim] ,'[', '.') ELSE jaql_table END AS Table, lookup([WIDGETS],WidgetId,_ID,_ID) AS WidgetID, CASE WHEN isnull([jaql_column]) OR [jaql_column] = '' THEN StrBetween([jaql_dim] ,'.', ']') ELSE jaql_column END AS Column from [Widgets.Widgets_panels_items]
Select distinct DashOwner, [_id], userId AS DashUser, oid AS DashboardId_, created, usageCount, upper([oid]) AS DashboardId from [DASHBOARDS_]
SELECT DISTINCT D.DashOwner [_ID], UA.ACTIVE, UA.CREATED, UA.EMAIL AS OWNER_EMAIL, UA.firstName AS OWNER_NAME, Role, userName FROM [DASHBOARDS] D JOIN [USER_ACTIONS] AS UA ON D.DashOwner = UA.[_ID]

SELECT [dashboards_].[_id] [_ID], created CREATED, [desc] AS [DESC], lastupdated LASTUPDATE, lastused LASTUSED, [dashboards_].TITLE TITLE, datasource_title AS Datasource_Title, datasource_address AS Datasource_Address, type TYPE, [dashboards_].source, ispublic, [dashboards_].oid, dashboardid, lastactiondate, days_since_last_use, eckey, dashowner FROM [dashboards_] WHERE Dash_Rank = 1

SELECT w._ID, CASE WHEN IsNullOrEmpty(w.DESCRIPTION) = TRUE THEN 'empty' ELSE w.DESCRIPTION END AS DESCRIPTION , w.INSTANCETYPE, w.lastUpdated_old, w.lastUsed_old, w.oid, w.TITLE, w.TYPE, w.dashboardid, w.CREATED, w.LASTUPDATED, w.LASTUSED, w.WidgetID, w.DashID, w.Dash_Widget, w.ElastiCube FROM WIDGETS_OLD W WHERE W.WidgetRank = 1
SELECT * FROM WIDGETS_OLD W WHERE W.WidgetRank = 1
